<style media="screen">
.fade-1 .content {
  background: rgba(33, 33, 33, .25) !important;
}
</style>



<body class="slides zoom horizontal noPreload animated ">

  <section class="slide fade-1 kenBurns slideWhite">
    <div class="content">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="wrap">

          <div class="fix-12-12 left">
            <ul class="flex reverse verticalCenter">
              <li class="col-12-12 left toRight section-header">
                <h3 class="small font-weight-bold ae-2 fromLeft section-title ">Section III</h3>
                <h5 class=" ae-2 fromLeft type-nunito left subtitle underline margin-bottom-5">
                  section recap and takeaways
                </h5>
                <h2 class="margin-bottom-5 ae-2 fromLeft">Let's review what we learned in this section.</h2>

                <ul class="grid">
                  <li class="col-6-12 left ae-4 fromAbove toLeft align-left ">
                    <h6 class=" ae-2 fromLeft text-yellow subtitle">Learning #1</h6>
                    <p class="ae-3 left">
                       Equity-minded practitioners are willing to take responsibility for the success of students from minoritized  racial/ethnic groups and critically assess their own beliefs and practices
                    </p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="col-6-12 left ae-4 fromAbove toLeft align-left ">
                    <h6 class=" ae-2 fromLeft text-yellow subtitle">Learning #2</h6>
                    <p class="ae-3 left">
                      Claiming not to ‘see race’, denying students’ racialized experiences, and saying that classrooms have no racial salience are actions that demonstrate a lack of equity-minded competence and undermine goals towards racial/ethnic equity.
                    </p>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="fix-12-12 center margin-top-5">
            <%= link_to title_4_path, class: "center button cueRed round gradient ae-3 circle" do %>
              Next Section <i class="fad fa-long-arrow-alt-right margin-left-1"></i>
            <% end %>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="background" style="background-image:url(https://www.sccpre.cat/mypng/full/145-1456885_moderate-red-curve-gradient-graphics-background-graphic.png);"></div>

  </section>

</body>
